              simultaneously, identifying themes, patterns, and relationships that would take humans weeks to discover. 
              <strong>It doesn't just sort‚Äîit understands.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Unlike simple keyword matching, AI organization uses <em>semantic clustering</em>. It knows that 
              "app is slow," "performance issues," and "takes forever to load" all belong in the same category. 
              It can even detect sentiment, urgency, and business impact to create multi-dimensional organization schemes.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 bg-purple-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-purple-100">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-purple-900 mb-4">Organization Dimensions</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
