                  <li>‚Ä¢ Content similarity</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Semantic relationships</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Subject matter clustering</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-purple-900 mb-2">By Business Impact</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-purple-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Customer segment affected</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Revenue implications</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Urgency indicators</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-purple-900 mb-2">By Sentiment</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-purple-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Positive vs negative feedback</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Frustration levels</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Satisfaction indicators</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-purple-900 mb-2">By Priority</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-purple-700 space-y-1">
