          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Transformation Power</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">From This:</h4>
              <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-3 border border-red-200">
                <p class="text-xs text-red-700">847 scattered feedback items in different formats, impossible to prioritize or act upon</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">To This:</h4>
              <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-3 border border-green-200">
                <p class="text-xs text-green-700">6 prioritized categories with clear business impact, customer segment analysis, and actionable roadmap</p>
