            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14-4H9m4 8H5m10-4h4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Multi-Dimensional</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Organizes by multiple criteria simultaneously: theme, priority, impact, sentiment</p>
          <div class="mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">4+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">Organization layers</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Insight -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">From Information to Intelligence</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        <span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Organization isn't just about filing‚Äîit's about strategic insight.</span>
        AI doesn't just sort your documents into neat piles. It reveals the strategic priorities, 
        hidden opportunities, and critical risks buried in your information overload.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">847</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Documents Processed ‚Üí 6 Strategic Categories</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">$1.2M</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Revenue Risk Identified & Prioritized</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">90%</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Reduction in Decision-Making Time</div>
